<h1>Post</h1>

<p>A new security hotfix for ColdFusion was released today:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.adobe.com/support/security/bulletins/apsb11-29.html">http://www.adobe.com/support/security/bulletins/apsb11-29.html</a></p>
<p>I'll use this as a reminder to folks to check out the <a href="http://hackmycf.com/">Hack My CF</a> service from Foundeo. It scans your ColdFusion servers, for free, and gives you a report of vulnerabilities. Most likely they already support this recent fix, and if not, they will soon.</p>
